ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: copyright
ivardefs.desc: A copyright statement relating to the implementation guide and/or its contents. Copyright statements are generally legal restrictions on the use and publishing of the implementation guide.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: The date  (and optionally time) when the implementation guide was published. The date must change when the business version changes and it must change if the status code changes. In addition, it should change when the substantive content of the implementa

ivardefs.name: definition
ivardefs.desc: The information needed by an IG publisher tool to publish the whole implementation guide.

ivardefs.name: dependsOn_
ivardefs.desc: Another implementation guide that this implementation depends on. Typically, an implementation guide uses value sets, profiles etc.defined in other implementation guides.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the implementation guide from a consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A Boolean value to indicate that this implementation guide is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing) and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: fhirVersion_
ivardefs.desc: The version(s) of the FHIR specification that this ImplementationGuide targets - e.g. describes how to use. The value of this element is the formal version of the specification, without the revision number, e.g. [publication].[major].[minor], which is 4.0

ivardefs.name: global_
ivardefs.desc: A set of profiles that all resources covered by this implementation guide must conform to.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A legal or geographic region in which the implementation guide is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: license
ivardefs.desc: The license that applies to this Implementation Guide, using an SPDX license code, or 'not-open-source'.

ivardefs.name: manifest
ivardefs.desc: Information about an assembled implementation guide, created by the publication tooling.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A natural language name identifying the implementation guide. This name should be usable as an identifier for the module by machine processing applications such as code generation.

ivardefs.name: packageId
ivardefs.desc: The NPM package name for this Implementation Guide, used in the NPM package distribution, which is the primary mechanism by which FHIR based tooling manages IG dependencies. This value must be globally unique, and should be assigned with care.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: The name of the organization or individual that published the implementation guide.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of this implementation guide. Enables tracking the life-cycle of the content.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive, user-friendly title for the implementation guide.

ivardefs.name: url

ivardefs.name: useContext_

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: The identifier that is used to identify this version of the implementation guide when it is referenced in a specification, model, design or instance. This is an arbitrary value managed by the implementation guide author and is not expected to be globally
